00:11.845 --> 00:14.139
♪ MIGHTY (LA, LA, HEY) ♪

00:14.222 --> 00:16.391
♪ MIGHTY (LA, LA, LA) ♪

00:16.474 --> 00:18.143
♪ COME ON, EVERYBODY,
MIGHTY B ♪

00:18.226 --> 00:21.187
♪ I GOT THE BEAT SO ALL THE KIDS
